    <p><strong>Branch naming konvence</strong> (CI kontrola v <code>.github/workflows/branch-check.yml</code>):</p>
    <pre><code># Formát: &#123;type&#125;/&#123;ITEM_ID&#125;-&#123;popis&#125;
git checkout -b feature/S-200-omop-parser
git checkout -b feature/F-102-anon-engine
git checkout -b defect/D-215-upload-validation
git checkout -b chore/T-050-ci-pipeline</code></pre>
    <p>Povolené typy: <code>feature</code>, <code>defect</code>, <code>hotfix</code>, <code>chore</code></p>

    <p><strong>Commit konvence:</strong></p>
    <pre><code>git commit -m "feat(S-200): implement OMOP CDM parser"
git commit -m "fix(S-215): validate upload file size"
git commit -m "test(S-201): add unit tests for parser"
git commit -m "docs(E-10): update epic hypothesis"</code></pre>
