    <h3>3.3 Kalibrace CW heuristik</h3>
    <p><strong>Claude Code (doporučeno):</strong></p>
    <pre><code>/edpa calibrate</code></pre>
    <p><strong>Manuální CLI:</strong></p>
    <pre><code>python3 .claude/edpa/scripts/evaluate_cw.py \
  --ground-truth .edpa/data/ground_truth.yaml \
  --heuristics .edpa/config/heuristics.yaml</code></pre>
    <p>Výstup:</p>
    <pre><code>MAD=0.041200
RECORDS=20
TOTAL_DEVIATION=0.824000</code></pre>

    <p><strong>Interpretace MAD (Mean Absolute Deviation):</strong></p>
    <div class="card">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>MAD</th><th>Hodnocení</th><th>Akce</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>&lt; 0.03</td><td style="color:var(--gn)">Výborné</td><td>Bez změny</td></tr>
          <tr><td>0.03 - 0.06</td><td style="color:var(--cy)">Dobré</td><td>Drobné korekce (volitelné)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>0.06 - 0.10</td><td style="color:var(--yl)">Přijatelné</td><td>Zvážit re-kalibraci signal weights</td></tr>
          <tr><td>&gt; 0.10</td><td style="color:var(--rd)">Špatné</td><td>Nutná kalibrace</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

